title: PML-N’s Muhammad Ashraf wins PP-138 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (PML-N) candidate, Muhammad Ashraf Rasool has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-138, Sheikhupura-III by securing 38,604 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was independent candidate, Abuzar Chadhar who bagged 33,073 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 48.79%.
